body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for reaching out to CarGo - your reliable car dealership! My name is Ethan Robinson. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Alexis! Before we proceed, could you please provide me with your phone number for contact purposes?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, my phone number is five five five - two three four - one zero zero one.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Alexis. Additionally, could you also share with me your email address, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, my email address is a dot b at example dot com.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for providing your contact information, Alexis. Your details will help us assist you better. Is there anything specific you'd like to discuss regarding our services today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm surprised by the shipping charges on my recent purchase.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand, Alexis. Let's address that concern for you. Thank you for sharing your feedback with us.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for your time, Alexis! If you need any further assistance, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
